{"tid":1031899,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三煞闖麥當勞 斬甩黑漢手指","createTime":"2019-02-22T03:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T04:23:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cc72806a41e589eded4230ffc6109907d44e9fd8","tid":1031899,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T03:28:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190222/20618222\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190222%2F20618222&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD1iy1AgKJyIubMvfhItfpFI%3D&h=97cd8fa0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190222%2F20618222&h=ed54e8df\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190222/20618222</a><br />\n<br />\n三煞闖麥當勞 斬甩黑漢手指<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190222/large/22la6p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190222%2Flarge%2F22la6p4.jpg&h=39c2fa3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n受傷黑漢送院命危。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名黑漢昨凌晨偕女友在長沙灣麥當勞快餐店用餐時，遭三名蒙面刀手闖入揮刀追斬，事主手腳中刀命危，其中右手尾指更被斬斷，兇徒傷人後乘私家車逃去，再縱火燒車毀滅證據。警方調查後懷疑涉及黑幫尋仇，正循線追查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190222/large/22la6p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190222%2Flarge%2F22la6p3.jpg&h=3307f326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員在案發麥當勞調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歹徒燒車滅迹<br />\n<br />\n26歲傷者姓卓，據悉有黑幫新義安背景，家住荃灣老圍，與女友拍拖一星期，案發前他帶女友找朋友後，到元州街416號麥當勞快餐店用餐。<br />\n<br />\n至昨凌晨近3時，消息稱，當時卓與女友剛用完餐準備離開，三名戴口罩及鴨舌帽男子，突然持牛肉刀由外衝入向他追斬，卓走避不及被斬傷手腳，右手尾指也被斬斷。兇徒傷人後跳上接應私家車逃去。警員及救護員接報到場，用冰塊包着斷指，再送院進行接駁手術，傷者經搶救後，情況危殆。<br />\n<br />\n其間，警方一度展開「捷進行動」，在長沙灣、荔枝角及葵涌等道路設路障，截查可疑車輛但無發現。至清晨6時許，警方在葵涌葵泰路發現涉案報失私家車遭人焚毀，警方調查後，案件列傷人及縱火案，由深水埗警區反三合會行動組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黃江奇、謝志輝  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n法政匯思：威脅任何在港人士<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n26年前劫案 被告：警揸睾丸逼供"},{"pid":"2316833c1633c47dc339b9da3f01734ed24c1996","tid":1031899,"uid":3820,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T03:31:23.000Z","msg":"仲以為nigga"},{"pid":"f8e0db810dde89628820c7e448ecae4f25806aa5","tid":1031899,"uid":154872,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2316833c1633c47dc339b9da3f01734ed24c1996","tid":1031899,"uid":3820,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T03:31:23.000Z","msg":"仲以為nigga"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T03:40:14.000Z","msg":"以為斬咗啲Kinder朱古力出嚟"},{"pid":"a008f31fafaf59463e044e60a40a1a499e264063","tid":1031899,"uid":49366,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T03:41:56.000Z","msg":"26年前劫案 被告：警揸睾丸逼供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16683936055fe1e0b51288557a0b35244a58196","tid":1031899,"uid":50328,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T03:54:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6103d42e1bfeea947236e78eb47faeb6ddfe6359","tid":1031899,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T04:00:13.000Z","msg":"經濟開始差<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要爭生意"},{"pid":"33f9ba69f55ff84525c3ed4d32edfd6e5fd45173","tid":1031899,"uid":66877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T04:17:45.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀間麥當勞 我睇既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724b24ad8c9439e9e7b7da5d1038179eb59a1a88","tid":1031899,"uid":38687,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a16683936055fe1e0b51288557a0b35244a58196","tid":1031899,"uid":50328,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2316833c1633c47dc339b9da3f01734ed24c1996","tid":1031899,"uid":3820,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T03:31:23.000Z","msg":"仲以為nigga"},"citedBy":1,"